  <Dialog id="10" name="MSG_009_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 10 4 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 0 0 0 11 0 0}...!?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="11" name="MSG_010_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 10 4 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 12 0 0}What the hell do you mean!?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="12" name="MSG_011_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 4 0 1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 13 0 0}He has the potential, and Ikutsuki-san approved it. He's a Persona-user now.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="13" name="MSG_012_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 10 3 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 14 0 0}I don't believe it...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 10 3 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 0 0 0 15 0 0}......[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="14" name="MSG_013_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 10 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 16 0 0}Tell me one more thing...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 10 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 17 0 0}Was it his decision to join?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="15" name="MSG_014_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 4 0 1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 18 0 0}Yeah. He came to us.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="16" name="MSG_015_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 10 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 19 0 0}I see...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 10 3 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 0 0 0 20 0 0}{f 4 23 0 1 3 25 25}......[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="17" name="MSG_015_5_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 10 3 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 21 0 0}Then... I guess I'll stick around.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="18" name="MSG_016_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 10 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 22 0 0}So, you're in charge now, huh?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="19" name="MSG_017_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 10 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 23 0 0}I got a question for you: What are you fighting for?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="20" name="SEL_018_0_0" type="Selection">
    <Option><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}To protect someone.]]></Option>
    <Option><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}For my own sake.]]></Option>
    <Option><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}I don't know.]]></Option>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="21" name="MSG_019_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 10 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 24 0 0}I see.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 10 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 25 0 0}Well, you do you.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 10 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 26 0 0}We gotta work together, either way.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="22" name="MSG_020_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 10 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 27 0 0}My old room still empty?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="23" name="MSG_021_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 4 0 1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 28 0 0}Yeah.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="24" name="MND_022_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="FFFF"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}Yet another new ally has joined.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="FFFF"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}Shinjiro Aragaki... He's a year older than me[n]and seems to have lived in the dorm before.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="FFFF"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}Though shrouded in mystery, he[n]seems to be a reliable partner...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
